Roth & Rau Supports Meyer Burger Bid, Recommends Shareholders to Accept

-- B y   R a j i v   S e k h r i
-- 
2011-05-16T07:23:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/roth-rau-supports-meyer-burger-bid-recommends-shareholders-to-accept.html
Roth & Rau AG (R8R)  support the buyout
offer of 22 euros a share from  Meyer Burger Technology AG. (MBTN)   The management and supervisory boards of Roth & Rau
recommend that shareholders accept the offer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rajiv Sekhri at 
 rsekhri1@bloomberg.net  